步履维艰，于是他自费上了编程补习班，工作之余便是看书学写代码。 同寝室的工友看到深圳还在埋头苦读的温学贵觉得不可思议，嘲笑他说“癞蛤蟆想吃天鹅肉”，你一个中专学历能有啥出息？ 最终，温学贵靠自己，成为一名微信小程序程序员，写字楼、电脑、月薪过万，这些他曾梦寐以求的东西，终于实现，而他也在备战自己的大专考试。（界面新闻）"},"attached_info":"Cj8Im7mYoe6Lj8czEAMaCDY0MDAyMDgwINHkwoQGMA441gVABXIJNDU3NzQ5NDMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"373 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c60034a3bb958bf798585db9c847d2e5_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1620140708.4380782","card_id":"Q_457684810","target":{"id":457684810,"title":"如何评价00后「坏小孩」演员们的演技？还有哪些演技很好的00后演员？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/457684810","type":"question","created":1620042441,"answer_count":107,"follower_count":357,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,1138,5419,26930,29916],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"从《隐秘的角落》、《唐人街探案》，到最近正在热映的《秘密访客》，这些电影里张子枫、荣梓杉、王圣迪等以「坏小孩」的路线，演绎出诡谲多变的荧幕形象，塑造的角色让人印象非常深刻。是否说明了这些零零后小演员的演技实力？ 一些年轻小演员们还正在上学，也不算科班出身，但目前来看已经有不少的电影作品，也和很多知名的老戏骨合作，为何电影会倾向于找这些小演员？如何评价他们的演技？还有哪些演技很好的00后演员，他们各有哪些代表作品？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Im7mYoe6Lj8czEAMaCDYzOTg3ODEzIMnFv4QGMAQ45QJABnIJNDU3Njg0ODEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"253 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-860299a1c7a8e8f9c4b1410e9c4e6d12_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1620140708.4386547","card_id":"Q_457347115","target":{"id":457347115,"title":"排位时五个射手可行吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/457347115","type":"question","created":1619798055,"answer_count":80,"follower_count":276,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[183735,399535,404003],"comment_count":6,"is_following":false,"excerpt"